The paper discusses low-complexity channel reconstruction methods for downlink precoding in massive MIMO systems, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG). However, since the focus is on channel reconstruction and precoding, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
